{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T18:01:53.057Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Interleaved Thinking"},{"type":"text","text":" is an advanced form of extended thinking that works specifically with tools—it enables Claude to think "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"between"},{"type":"text","text":" tool calls, reflecting on results and strategically planning the next action rather than just chaining tools together blindly."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Interleaved Thinking is extended thinking with tool use in Claude 4 models that enables Claude to think between tool calls and evaluate results before determining the next step."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Unlike traditional AI reasoning where Claude had to plan all tool calls upfront, Interleaved Thinking allows Claude to:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Think first"},{"type":"text","text":" → reason about the problem\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Call a tool"},{"type":"text","text":" → get results\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Think again"},{"type":"text","text":" → evaluate what it discovered\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Call another tool"},{"type":"text","text":" → based on new insights\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Repeat"},{"type":"text","text":" → adapting dynamically"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Difference: Before vs Now"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Before (Traditional)"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now (Interleaved Thinking)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write all questions BEFORE going to library"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Formulate new questions based on discoveries"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Plan all tool calls upfront"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think between each tool call"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Rigid, sequential tool execution"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Adaptive, dynamic reasoning"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Predict every scenario from start"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Respond intelligently to what's discovered"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How It Works"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Pattern: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"think → tool → think → tool → reply"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Start: User asks complex question\n   ↓\n2. Think: Claude reasons about what it knows/needs\n   ↓\n3. Tool: Call first tool (e.g., search database)\n   ↓\n4. Think: Reflect on results, spot anomalies\n   ↓\n5. Tool: Call second tool based on insights\n   ↓\n6. Think: Analyze new findings\n   ↓\n7. Reply: Deliver final insights"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Advantages of Interleaved Thinking"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Advantage"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Impact"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reasoning Between Actions"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude reflects on tool results before determining next step"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Intelligent Tool Chaining"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Multiple tools interconnected through reasoning, not just automation"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Refined Decision-Making"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Choices based on intermediate outcomes, not just initial info"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Real-World Example"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Data analysis workflow:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Claude retrieves campaign data from BigQuery\n   ↓\n2. Analyzes outcomes, spots anomalies\n   ↓\n3. Chooses logical investigation route\n   ↓\n4. Executes additional analysis\n   ↓\n5. Reflects on findings\n   ↓\n6. Delivers insights"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Result: \"Like having a cursor for data analysis\" where each step is guided by genuine thought rather than preset logic."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How to Enable It"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Option 1: Standard Extended Thinking with Tools"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"response = client.messages.create(\n    model=\"claude-sonnet-4-20250514\",  # Claude 4 model required\n    max_tokens=16000,\n    thinking={\"type\": \"enabled\", \"budget_tokens\": 8000},\n    tool_choice={\"type\": \"auto\"},\n    tools=[search_tool, database_tool],\n    messages=[{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"...\"}]\n)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Option 2: Adaptive Thinking (auto-enables interleaved)"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"response = client.messages.create(\n    model=\"claude-opus-4-6\",  # Claude 4.6+ model\n    max_tokens=16000,\n    thinking={\"type\": \"enabled\", \"adaptive\": True},  # Automatically enables interleaved thinking\n    tool_choice={\"type\": \"auto\"},\n    tools=[...]\n)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Required header"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"anthropic-beta: extended-thinking-202505-14"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Which Models Support It"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Model Type"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Interleaved Thinking"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude 4 models"},{"type":"text","text":" (Opus 4, Sonnet 4)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ Supported"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude 4.5+ models"},{"type":"text","text":" (Sonnet 4.5, Opus 4.1)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ Supported"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude 4.6+ models"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ Adaptive thinking auto-enables it"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude 3.7 Sonnet"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"⚠️ Extended thinking only (no interleaved)"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to Use Interleaved Thinking"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Ideal for:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Complex workflows"},{"type":"text","text":" requiring adaptive reasoning and tool coordination\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-step research"},{"type":"text","text":" where findings inform next steps\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Data analysis"},{"type":"text","text":" needing anomaly detection and investigation\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Debugging"},{"type":"text","text":" with multi-level error causes\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"System design"},{"type":"text","text":" requiring weighing multiple options"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Not needed for:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Simple tool calls (no reasoning required)\n- Single-tool tasks\n- High-volume low-latency applications"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Benefits Over Basic Extended Thinking"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":